<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>I bless Your Name</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 I lenkers bånd - i mørket satt
 Paulus, Silas ba den natt
 Og i sin smertes gru de sang
 Og de ble løst - i Jesu Navn

[C1]
   Kor: Å kjære Navn - Å kjære Navn
   Jeg gir all ære og min sang
   Du er jo Livet, Du er sann
   Å kjære navn - Det Jesu Navn

[V2]
 Om du en natt - blir buret inn
 Og du er fange i ditt sinn
 Rekk ut og pris Ham - vær i brann
 For lenker faller i Hans Navn

[V3]
 In prisoners' chains
 With bleeding stripes
 Paul and Silas prayed that night
 And in their pain began to sing
 Their chains were loosed
 And they were free

[C2]
   I bless Your Name
   I bless Your Name
   I give You honor, give You praise
   You are the Life, the Truth, the Way
   I bless Your Name
   I bless Your Name

[V4]
 Some midnight hour
 If you should find
 You're in a prison in your mind
 Reach out and praise
 Defy those chains
 And they will fall
 In Jesus' Name

[C3]
   We bless Your Name
   We bless Your Name
   We give You honor, give You praise
   You are the Life, the Truth, the Way
   We bless Your Name
   We bless Your Name</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<aka>Å kjære Navn</aka>
<presentation>v1 c1 v2 c1 v3 c2 v4 c3</presentation>
</song>